    <description>From the website....&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;quot;Zanzibar!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Just saying the word makes you think of far off places and high adventure. Okay, maybe not so much if you&amp;rsquo;re a Poor Bloody Infantryman but for an Officer and a Gentleman the &amp;ldquo;Age of Imperialism&amp;rdquo; (1850 &amp;ndash; 1914) was the best of times.&amp;#10;A time where young men could garner fame and fortune in dark and dangerous lands. A time where heroes could be made in a day. And a time where death could come swiftly and from unexpected places.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Colonial Adventures allows you to recreate these &amp;ldquo;dirty little wars&amp;rdquo; of European expansion on the tabletop. Refight the heroic stand at Rourke&amp;rsquo;s Drift or try and change the result at Isandhlwana. But it isn&amp;rsquo;t just about the British and Zulus. It&amp;rsquo;s also about the French Foreign Legion, Berber horsemen, Imperial German forces, Masai warriors, the Russian army, Pathan tribesmen, and much more.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Whether you&amp;rsquo;re an experienced Colonials player or a novice just starting the period, Colonial Adventures is right for you. Here&amp;rsquo;s just a few reasons why.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;     In the book you&amp;rsquo;ll find over a dozen armies to choose from and another twenty online.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;     We&amp;rsquo;ve included &amp;ldquo;open ended&amp;rdquo; scenarios to fight new and unique battles every time you use them.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;     You can play solo, all on the same side against the game, or head to head.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;     We provide online support to answer any questions you may have as they come up and usually in less than 24 hours.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;So have a seat, grab a spot of tea, and get ready for hours of fun. Welcome to the world of ...&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Colonial Adventures!&amp;quot;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;These miniatures rules are available in print and PDF.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
